OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy rain
OL,6,Fbecoming mostly confined to south
OL,7,FWales this evening with lighter,
OL,8,Fpatchier rain lingering further north.
OL,9,FRain generally easing during the early
OL,10,Fhours. Winds falling lighter too. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FFriday looks mostly cloudy
OL,13,Fwith some light drizzly rain on and
OL,14,Foff during the morning. Some heavier
OL,15,Foutbreaks of rain are possible during
OL,16,Fthe afternoon. Breezy at times. Less
OL,17,Fmild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
