OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FOvernight rain soon clearing to
OL,7,Flengthy sunny periods on Saturday with
OL,8,Fisolated showers. Turning damp and
OL,9,Fwindy on Sunday. Further showery rain
OL,10,Fon Monday, and still breezy. Staying
OL,11,Fmild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
